public abstract class AutomatonOperationAction<T extends Automaton,O extends Automaton>
extends EditableAction<T,O>

This is an abstract action for operations on automata that will produce new automata. This action will check the validity of the automaton in the pre-process and lay out the automaton in the post-process.

Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
